     A          R GDGPR891
     A                                     2'GDGR8A'
     A                                      SKIPB(2)
     A                                    20'ASJ KANBAN REISSUE(PART):'
     A                                    +1'IAF -> AOYAMA SEISAKUSHO'
     A                                    46'DATE :'
